xt-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Jimmy Hotz\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| ''Beyond the Crystal Sea''\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Album\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Top 100 Christian Rock Albums of All Time No. 98,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hmmagazine.com/blog/hm-exclusives/top-100-christian-rock-albums-of-all-time/ |title=Top 100 Christian Rock Albums of All Time, No. 98 Beyond the Crystal Sea \u2013 Jimmy Hotz}}</ref> & CCM's 500 Best Albums Of All Time No. 210<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ccms500bestalbums.wordpress.com/?s=Jimmy+Hotz |title=CCM's 500 Best Albums of All Time, 210. Beyond the Crystal Sea \u2013 Jimmy Hotz}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| 1980\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| ArkAngel\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| ''Warrior''\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Album\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Top 100 Christian Rock Albums of All Time No. 87,<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://hmmagazine.com/blog/hm-exclusives/top-100-christian-rock-albums-of-all-time/ |title=Top 100 Christian Rock Albums of All Time, No. 87 Warrior \u2013 ArkAngel}}</ref> & CCM's 500 Best Albums Of All Time No. 106<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://ccms500bestalbums.wordpress.com/?s=Arkangel |title=CCM's 500 Best Albums of All Time, 106. Warrior \u2013 Arkangel}}</ref>\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| 1981\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Speedy West, Jr.\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| ''Used Guitars''\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Album\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| \u2013\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| 1981\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| Austin O'Neal\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| \"Someone has to Lose\"\n| style=\"text-align:left; vertical-align:top;\"| 